Package: TRexSelector
Type: Package
Title: T-Rex Selector: High-Dimensional Variable Selection & FDR
        Control
Version: 2.0.0
Description: FDR-controlled variable selection for regression and classification in
 high-dimensional settings while controlling the false discovery rate (FDR) at a user-specified
 target level. The R package comes as R bindings to the TRexSelector C++ library.
